title: Bobby Forgot His Wedding Ring to Dinner + Travis Denning performs “TV Themes” From A Hat on Guitar + Lunchbox Offers To Put Sunscreen on Random People
itunes:title: Bobby Forgot His Wedding Ring to Dinner + Travis Denning performs “TV Themes” From A Hat on Guitar + Lunchbox Offers To Put Sunscreen on Random People
description:
Bobby tells us about what happened when he forgot to wear his wedding ring to dinner. Travis Denning stops by to talk about his new project and tries to play TV Theme songs that Bobby draws from a hat. Amy told us about a PayPal scam she almost got tricked into. So Lunchbox went after the scammers behind it to see if it was legit or not.
